<section id="why-choose-us" class="section why-choose-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us</h2>
    <div class="why-choose-grid">
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M19 21l-7-5-7 5V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Industry Compliance</h3>
        <p>Adhering to strict protocols for government, healthcare, and legal sectors, ensuring all deliveries meet regulatory requirements.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Proactive Issue Resolution</h3>
        <p>Our team anticipates and addresses potential challenges before they affect your deliveries, ensuring smooth operations.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="16 12 12 8 8 12"></polyline>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="8"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strategic Nationwide Coverage</h3>
        <p>Our extensive network ensures we can reach every corner of Malaysia efficiently, even remote locations.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Secure Document Handling</h3>
        <p>State-of-the-art security measures for confidential documents, protecting your sensitive information at all times.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
        <p>We're committed to giving back to the communities we serve through various initiatives and sustainable practices.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="why-choose-item">
        <div class="why-choose-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Dedicated Customer Support</h3>
        <p>Our responsive team is available to address your queries and concerns promptly, ensuring a seamless experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-choose-section {
    background-color: var(--color-light-gray);
  }
  
  .why-choose-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .why-choose-item {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .why-choose-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .why-choose-icon {
    background-color: rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.1);
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .why-choose-item h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .why-choose-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-choose-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>